quotes.author: Oscar Wilde
quotes.content: Be yourself; everyone else is already taken.

quotes.author: Mark Twain
quotes.content: If you tell the truth, you don't have to remember anything.

quotes.author: Elbert Hubbard
quotes.content: A friend is someone who knows all about you and still loves you.

quotes.author: J.K. Rowling
quotes.content: It does not do to dwell on dreams and forget to live.

quotes.author: Thomas Sowell
quotes.content: When you want to help people, you tell them the truth. When you want to help yourself, you tell them what they want to hear.
